Parameters:
requestId - Verification Request Identifier
accountId - Account ID the request was for
status - Latest status of the verification request
number - Number this verification request is for.
price - The price charged for the verification request.
currency - Currency code.
senderId - Actual sender_id used for SMS attempts.
dateSubmitted - Date the Verification Request was submitted.
dateFinalized - Date the Verification Request was either successfully checked or failed.
firstEventSent - Time first attempt was made.
lastEventSent - Time last attempt was made.
checks - List of checks made for this verification and their outcomes.
errorText - If an error occurred, this will explain in readable terms the error encountered.
